snippet: Al Horford's follow shot with 1.3 seconds left gave the Boston Celtics a 94-92 victory over the Detroit Pistons on Saturday night....
lead_paragraph: Al Horford's follow shot with 1.3 seconds left gave the Boston Celtics a 94-92 victory over the Detroit Pistons on Saturday night.

headline.main: Celtics Win in Detroit on Horford's Follow in Final Seconds
